title: Amazon Overhauls Delivery Network to Dispatch Packages Faster, More Cheaply
description: The company’s changes have cut delivery times, transformed inventory management and altered the search results customers see on its flagship e-commerce website.

title: TikTok Feeds Teens a Diet of Darkness
description: Self-harm, sad-posting and disordered-eating videos abound on the popular app.

title: Help! My Political Beliefs Were Altered by a Chatbot!
description: AI assistants may be able to change our views without our realizing it. Says one expert: “What’s interesting here is the subtlety.”
